OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fwarm evening to end Monday, though any
OL,7,Flate sunshine may be rather hazy. Low
OL,8,Fcloud and fog spreading inland from
OL,9,Fthe west overnight, bringing mist and
OL,10,Fmurk by dawn plus spots of drizzle. A
OL,11,Fmild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FLow cloud retreating to
OL,14,Fwestern coasts during the morning,
OL,15,Fwhere it may linger throughout
OL,16,FTuesday. Elsewhere, a very warm day
OL,17,Fwith spells of strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
